 _8"></span>藏传佛教的修行人，<span class="_ _8"></span>不仅仅是实</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y20d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">修，<span class="_ _6"></span>还要在二三十年的时间里，<span class="_ _8"></span>依靠辩论、<span class="_ _6"></span>研讨、<span class="_ _8"></span>分析等方</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y20e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">式，精通各种理论。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 y20f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我去过很多学校，<span class="_ _a"></span>但像藏地那样的学习方式，<span class="_ _a"></span>现在还为</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y210 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">数不多。<span class="_ _6"></span>当然，<span class="_ _8"></span>我不是说只应该修持、<span class="_ _6"></span>不能研究，<span class="_ _8"></span>而是既要</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
